name: White Hare of Inaba
skill: Increases DMG dealt by 2 allies (melee priority) by 45%/55% for a limited time.

additional_data.description: A rabbit spirit who received the grace of a god. She's conviced the vivid dreams she has whenever she takes a nap are trying to tell her something. Unfortunately, they have an uncanny knack of ending before the most important part, and as a result are totally useless.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Jewel Summon
◦ Obtained as a Login Reward (Day 7)
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ At the beginning of the game, her name was "Inaba Whitehare"

main: "Eeep! I've got a bad feeling about this..."
skill: "I know--I'll count how many times I splat you!"
summon: "I've a feeling good things'll happen if I stick with you!"
